long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Probook automates dispatching for home service businesses, including HVAC, Plumbing, and Electrical companies. Probook uses AI to match technicians to the right calls based on historical data and routing optimization, helping home service businesses dispatch more profitably. Probook accomplishes this via Chrome extension that lays directly over your CRM screen.
